  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4c24e01ed0a48f14a8ec8de924835528, type: 3}
  m_Name: PaginaLichenia
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  thoughts:
  - I met Madame Lichenia. Or maybe she met me first. She is not the kind of fortune teller you find at night fairs. There is something vegetal about her, almost mineral, as if she grew there between the leaves and the webs. She did not ask me anything. She simply knew. And when she asked if I wanted my fortune read, it felt as though she had already written it.
